      "content": "i see. it's interesting you mention \"progressive educational institutions\" like that. does that mean the arguments against it are mostly coming from people who aren't part of the actual educational field, or are there professional educators who think this is a bad idea too? i'm trying to figure out if the opposition is based on professional concerns or just social/political ones.",
